  - Visual feedback via color change and content update in the bucket to indicate whether the value was successfully added or if a collision occurred.
  - Feedback messages that guide users based on their actions.

#### Layout Description:
- The layout provides a clear, structured space:
  - Text and controls are centered and spaciously arranged to ensure a clean look.
  - Safe area margins of **24px** on all sides provide ample space for visual comfort.
  - Each section has **16px** padding for separation, maintaining clarity and focus.
  - The hash table is visually distinct from the input section, ensuring that users can easily navigate the interactive components while maintaining a logical flow of information.
  - The container and sections are responsive and adapt to different screen sizes.

This interactive module effectively embodies an engaging hands-on learning experience centered around the concept of hash tables, providing users with an intuitive understanding of a pivotal algorithm in computer science.

